<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />My tears have been my food day and night,</para>

<para style="q1">while my enemies are always saying to me, "Where is your God?"</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />These things I call to mind as I pour out my soul:</para>

<para style="q1">how I went with the throng and led them to the house of God</para>

<para style="q1">with the voice of joy and praise, a multitude celebrating a festival.</para>
